{"tid":2452044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國邊境現20年最大偷渡潮 拜登喊:「不要再來了」","createTime":"2021-03-18T14:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T19:33:28.000Z","uid":318316,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c1cef109c827bde7eea8f3285961438de06d22d8","tid":2452044,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"美國南部接壤墨西哥的邊界近來湧入大量移民，其中包括數以千計無人陪伴的孩童，外界批評聲浪隨之升高，總統拜登（JoeBiden）今天特別呼籲移民「別來美國」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登接受美國廣播公司新聞網（ABC News）訪問時向移民喊話：「是的，我可以很明白地說，不要過來&hellip;不要離開你的城鎮、城市或社區。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登受訪的數小時前，國土安全部長才發布聲明捍衛拜登政府的移民政策。外界批評拜登摒棄前總統川普（Donald Trump）的強硬立場，變相鼓勵了這波移民潮，對此拜登不予理會，表示2019年和2020年都有類似的移民激增現象。<br />\n<br />\n拜登指出，自己最近聽到一種說法，這些移民之所以會來美國「是因為他們覺得我是好人」，但拜登不認同這種說法，並提到政府正在遣返穿越邊界的人。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5324456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F5324456&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSgKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=8dd8fd67\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5324456</a>"},{"pid":"8ca8749504407186a8e9d4bcf380fc3fb835d424","tid":2452044,"uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2b37062ceb2d8a3111539c0a45a125e74fddd6","tid":2452044,"uid":204929,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"左膠:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84R4HZD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84R4HZD.jpg&h=85c4d545&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca399b01bc73b826180617165c4e6b3a88721f02","tid":2452044,"uid":254165,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"歧視難民？<img src=\"/ass